</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>The summary looks great Murtak. You seem to have gotten to the core of the issues.<br />
<br />
My addendum:<br />
<br />
I would like to raise my voice for the changes, when and if they come, to be <b>available to a wide range of players</b>. Not just the uber-guilders.<br />
<br />
My feeling is that spells should be roughly the same for everyone but gear should set people apart.<br />
<br />
If SoE does not make the same spells available to everyone, <b>some people will end up being less</b> shaman than other shaman. Spells are what makes us shaman, gear and skills is what make us uber. <b>Restricting key-spells for only a few is bordering on segregation.</b><br />
<br />
AA's are more fair since everyone can with a little time put into it aquire the AA's the prioritize. Still. Thats a lame excuse for key abilites.</p>
	
	
	
