	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I agree, we need more burst damage, but we also need it to be sustainable.  I'm digging hard to find out <b>how much</b> burst damage we feel is acceptable over what amount of time and then see if it can be balanced against the true "DPS" classes and not turn us into gods.<br />
<br />
The best chance of us getting changes are to stay within the framework of spells we already have and tune things.  Thus a hard look at Rains.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
