	<p>i defininitely like all the things you referred to Murtak, especially the group heal, of course we all know that Quiescence, our heal over time spells, are most mana efficient and do a great job also... a group heal over time would be awesome.. even if it was like a 30 minute reuse it would still be awesome... spear of torment, definitely needs to be increased in damage, even if the mana was significantly increased, with all of my spell crit aa's, i crit quite a bit, does some pretty decent damage compared to dots especially if you have the mana saving focus..<br />
<br />
The idea of the basically... cannibalizing your health for others safety, alot like the paladin AA act of valor, i think that is also a good idea, developers should definitely think about that.  Could come in very handy, nice work Murtak.</p>
	
	
	
